Package: lapop
Type: Package
Title: Creates Visualizations Using LAPOP Styles 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Luke Plutowski, LAPOP Lab
Maintainer: Luke Plutowski <Luke.Plutowski@vanderbilt.edu>
Description: This package creates visualizations that follow LAPOP's style guidelines and formatting for use in reports, presentations, and social media posts.  
    IMPORTANT: Run lapop_fonts() before creating any graphs in order to use LAPOP-standard fonts.
URL: https://github.com/lapop-central/lapop-viz
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.3.0) 
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
